{ This move amounts to Black winning an exchange. White gets great long-term compensation. }
7. Bxf5 e6 { The main move is  7...Qxa1. } 8. Nd2
{ Of course, if White retreats his bishop his compensation for the exchange would be dubious, since Black was allowed to play ...e6. }
