c5 9. c4 Nc6 10. Ngf3 Nge7 11. dxc5
{ Another strong idea - once Black has blocked his f8-bishop, take on c5 so that Black is forced to retake with the queen. }
11... Qxc5 12. O-O Ng6 13. Rfe1
