14... Bxc2 { 14...Nd3+?  15.Bxd3  Qxf4  doesn't work because of  16.Rf1!. } 15.
dxe5 { 15.Qxc2?  Nf3+  followed by ...Qxf4 is Black's idea. } 15... Bxd1 16.
exd6 Bg4 17. Bd3
{ Now White has a significantly stronger version of the same endgame. White is better. }
