16. Nd2 Bxc5
{ This seems by force to lead to an endgame that is preferable for White. Perhaps  16...O-O  is better -  17.Nb3  Nc4 !  18.Bxc4  dxc4  19.Na5  is very unclear to me. }
17. Bxc5 Rxc5 18. Nb3 Rxc3 { Or  18...Nxb3  19.axb3  Rxc3 } 19. Kd2 Nxb3+
