axb3 Rxb3 21. Rxa7 Ke7 { White was threatening Ra8+. } 22. Rxb7 Kd6 23. Ra1
{ Intending Ra6+ and/or Raa7. } 23... Rb2+ 24. Ke3 Re8+ 25. Kd4 Rxf2 26. Ra6+
Ke7 27. Raa7 Rd8 28. Ke3 Rf6
